release.description:
# v0.9.2 (2019.04.09)

### Features

- Able to change/edit account name in accountDetails page

### Fixes

- change staking and spending token ids
- Fix switch local network some time not working issue
- Fix switch network apiRemote not re-connect issue
- Able to display custom tokens

![longAccountName](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/205194/55761135-6e235a80-5ab2-11e9-9652-8798b61d8df6.gif)
![accountName](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/205194/55761136-6e235a80-5ab2-11e9-9896-0dcd0e73f957.gif)
